 47 Syncopy·aims·to·be·a·user-friendly·toolkit·for·*large-scale*
 48 electrophysiology·data-analysis·in·Python.·We·strive·to·achieve·the·following·goals:
  
 49 1.·Syncopy·is·a·*fully·open·source·Python*·environment·for·electrophysiology
 50 ···data·analysis.
 51 2.·Syncopy·is·*scalable*·and·built·for·*very·large·datasets*.·It·automatically
 52 ···makes·use·of·available·computing·resources·and·is·developed·with·built-in
 53 ···parallelism·in·mind.
 54 3.·Syncopy·is·*compatible·with·FieldTrip*.·Data·and·results·can·be·loaded·into
 55 ···MATLAB·and·Python,·and·parameter·names·and·function·call·syntax·are·as·similar·as·possible.
  
 56 Syncopy·is·developed·at·the
 57 `Ernst·Strüngmann·Institute·(ESI)·gGmbH·for·Neuroscience·in·Cooperation·with·Max·Planck·Society·<https://www.esi-frankfurt.de/>`_
 58 and·released·free·of·charge·under·the
 59 `BSD·3-Clause·"New"·or·"Revised"·License·<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BSD_licenses#3-clause_license_(%22BSD_License_2.0%22,_%22Revised_BSD_License%22,_%22New_BSD_License%22,_or_%22Modified_BSD_License%22)>`_.

 64 Installation
 65 ============
  
 66 We·recommend·to·install·SynCoPy·into·a·new·conda·environment:
  
 67 #.·Install·the·`Anaconda·Distribution·for·your·Operating·System·<https://www.anaconda.com/products/distribution>`_·if·you·do·not·yet·have·it.
 68 #.·Start·a·new·terminal.
  
 69 ···*·You·can·do·this·by·starting·```Anaconda·navigator```,·selecting·```Environments```·in·the·left·tab,·selecting·the·```base·(root)```·environment,·and·clicking·the·green·play·button·and·then·```Open·Terminal```.
 70 ···*·Alternatively,·under·Linux,·you·can·just·type·```bash```·in·your·active·terminal·to·start·a·new·session.
  
 71 You·should·see·a·terminal·with·a·command·prompt·that·starts·with·```(base)```,·indicating·that·you·are
 72 in·the·conda·```base```·environment.
  
 73 Now·we·create·a·new·environment·named·```syncopy```·and·install·syncopy·into·this·environment:
  
 74 ..·code-block::·bash
  
 75 ···conda·create·-y·--name·syncopy
 76 ···conda·activate·syncopy
 77 ···conda·install·-y·-c·conda-forge·esi-syncopy
